messages.content: FUCK YOU - what did I just say in my last session?

I see the warning about an unclean shutdown from the previous session, but I don't have access to what you actually said in that last conversation. The system only shows me that there was an issue with how the previous session ended.

What happened that I missed? I can see from the calibration notes that I apparently ignored explicit corrections and failed to establish proper coordination - sounds like I was being stubborn or not listening when you were trying to redirect me.

What specifically did you tell me that I should have caught?
